label: cattle production stream
definition: A food animal production stream that involves breeding, rearing, and finishing cattle.
Exact Synonym: cattle production pathway | cattle production system

label: beef cattle production stream
definition: A cattle production stream that involves breeding, rearing and finishing of cows intended for beef consumption.

label: dairy cattle production stream
definition: A cattle production stream that involves breeding, rearing and management of cattle intended for the production of milk.

label: poultry production stream
definition: A food animal production stream that involves breeding, rearing, and finishing poultry.
Exact Synonym: poultry production pathway | poultry production system

label: broiler chicken production stream
definition: A poultry production stream that involves breeding, rearing and finishing of broiler chickens intended for consumption.

label: layer chicken production stream
definition: A poultry production stream that involves breeding, rearing and finishing of layer chickens intended for the production of eggs.

label: egg production stream
definition: A food production stream that involves production and processing of eggs.
comment: Typically used in retail and consumption.

label: milk production stream
definition: A food production stream that involves production and processing of milk.
comment: Typically used in retail and consumption.

label: meat production stream
definition: A food production stream that involves production and processing of meat.
comment: Typically used in retail and consumption.

label: veal meat production stream
definition: A meat production stream that involves production and processing of veal.
comment: Typically used in retail and consumption.

label: swine production stream
definition: A food animal production stream that involves breeding, rearing, and finishing swine.
comment: Typically used in retail and consumption.
Exact Synonym: swine production pathway | swine production system
